# +SolarControl Page Refinement: Implementation Guide (Concept A)

## 1. Overview

This document provides the complete content and structural specifications for implementing the **Concept A: The Accordion Stack** redesign of the +SolarControl product page. The content is sourced from the approved copy brief and the current live website, consolidated into the new, more compact structure.

This guide is intended to be used directly for development, with all copy and component details provided.

---

