#### Accordion Panel 2: Industrial Hardware

**Title:** `‚ñ∂ Industrial Hardware Built for RES Plants`

**Expanded Content:**

**Subheadline:**

```
No vendor lock-in. No commercial protocol limitations.
```

**Body:**

```
At the core of +SolarControl is an industrial MiniPC with custom firmware, housed in a sealed, pre-wired panel built to EN IEC 61439-1 & EN 61439-5 standards. It installs in minutes, operates in extreme temperatures (-20 to +60¬∞C) and securely manages all communication with field devices.
```

**Feature List (Two Columns):**

**Column 1:**

- **Custom Firmware:** OTA updates & flexible configuration

- **Edge Controller:** unique identifier & VPN client for secure access

- **Zero-Trust Security:** impervious to cyberattacks & tampering attempts

- **Industrial Durability:** certified, sealed, mechanically protected

**Column 2:**

- Compatibility with 65+ inverter manufacturers

- Support for all major open protocols (IEC-60870-5-104, Modbus TCP/RTU, IEC61850, OPC-UA/DA/XML-DA)

- Sealed enclosure for physical protection

- Integration with aggregators & ready for storage/BESS control

- API for future interoperability

